__NAME__ purpose
CSS class to designate problems
__END__

__NAME__ synopsis
<group choice='req'>
	<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>class</replaceable></arg>
</group>
__END__

__NAME__ description
<literal>CSS_CONTRAST</literal> is used by &tag-error; and &tag-formel; to
designate problems. Both use <literal>mv_contrast</literal> as default if
<literal>CSS_CONTRAST</literal> has no value.
__END__

__NAME__ example
<programlisting>
Variable CSS_CONTRAST error
</programlisting>
__END__

__NAME__ see also
error, formel
__END__